            <title>1.8.9</title>
            <pubDate>Sun, 19 Jul 2026 14:22:42 +0000</pubDate>
            <sparkle:version>10809999</sparkle:version>
            <sparkle:shortVersionString>1.8.9</sparkle:shortVersionString>
            <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>10.15</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
            <description><![CDATA[<h2>What's New</h2>
<h3>Fixes</h3>
<ul>
<li><strong>The preferences window no longer keeps popping up every few seconds</strong> — When "Launch &amp; Quit with Player" was enabled, the background helper crashed every time it tried to hand control back to the system, so macOS kept relaunching it, and every relaunch reopened the already-running app and pulled up the preferences window. The helper now exits cleanly and skips relaunching the app when it is already running.</li>
</ul>]]></description>
            <enclosure url="https://github.com/MxIris-LyricsX-Project/LyricsX/releases/download/v1.8.9/LyricsX_1.8.9+10809999.zip" length="8857029" type="application/octet-stream" sparkle:edSignature="6ebidJfn7dctiQ+WNJKc6G4mAAaSUFwX4apiTB5QtdOxR4bKpz3ihKD0Pu7ZMgbJ9hMlQJmpVGx4ptCRYBsNAA==" />
        </item>
        <item>
            <title>1.9.0-beta.10</title>
            <pubDate>Tue, 30 Jun 2026 16:23:26 +0000</pubDate>
            <sparkle:channel>beta</sparkle:channel>
            <sparkle:version>10900110</sparkle:version>
            <sparkle:shortVersionString>1.9.0-beta.10</sparkle:shortVersionString>
            <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>12.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
            <description><![CDATA[<h2>What's New</h2>
<h3>New</h3>
<ul>
<li><strong>Apple Music lyrics source</strong> — LyricsX can now fetch lyrics from Apple Music. To use it, sign in to Apple Music in your browser, find the `media-user-token` value in the site's cookies, then paste that token into LyricsX preferences.</li>
</ul>]]></description>
            <enclosure url="https://github.com/MxIris-LyricsX-Project/LyricsX/releases/download/v1.9.0-beta.10/LyricsX_1.9.0-beta.10+10900110.zip" length="9534071" type="application/octet-stream" sparkle:edSignature="vjdUCkJvmayZnWR6BI6Vm37zFtgev+q/2HatGYBlG+2H6Z32WomE5Q+al/tY9wkrDIjAgeHRFF3r7OcY4VWBCg==" />
