            <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>10.15</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
            <description><![CDATA[<h2>LyricsX 1.8.6 What's New</h2>
<h3>Fixes</h3>
<ul>
<li><strong>Fixed desktop lyrics flickering</strong> — The desktop line-by-line lyrics no longer flicker about once a second during playback (an issue that could also trigger a brief line-change-like animation). Lyrics now track playback smoothly again.</li>
</ul>
<h3>System Requirements</h3>
<ul>
<li>Minimum requirement: <strong>macOS 10.15 (Catalina)</strong></li>
</ul>]]></description>
